        "parts": [
          {
            "text": "Here are some of the best facial spas near Houston, TX, based on recent reviews and articles:\n\n*   **Organic Spa Houston:** This spa is known for top-notch skincare and beauty services, including facials, brows, and lashes. It has received several accolades, including being named \"Best Brows and Lash Service\" by KPRC Channel 2 Houston in 2023 and recognition from Modern Luxury Magazine as a top health and beauty expert since 2016.\n*   **Vera Pelle European Skin Spa:** This spa specializes in holistic facials, face lifting, and buccal massages. They offer a range of European facials and facial massage techniques, as well as treatments for various skin concerns like anti-aging, redness, acne, and hyperpigmentation.\n*   **Persona Med Spa:** Established in 2001, Persona Med Spa is considered Houston's first dedicated med spa. They offer a combination of medical treatments, traditional spa services, and health and wellness consultations.\n*   **True Skin Aesthetics:** This med spa is dedicated to addressing the skincare needs of people of color. They provide treatments like microdermabrasion, dermaplaning, chemical peels, and laser skin resurfacing.\n*   **Aesthetic Atelier:** This professional med spa offers a range of aesthetic and wellness services, including wrinkle relaxers, facial fillers, facials, Hydrafacials, and microneedling.\n*   **River Oaks Galleria Med Spa:** This med spa, medically directed by Dr. Agnes Usoro-Umoh, offers personalized treatment plans and cutting-edge technology to deliver natural results. Services include facial balancing, laser therapies, hair restoration, and IV hydration.\n*   **Pure Spa at Marriott Marquis Houston:** Located within the Marriott Marquis, Pure Spa offers a variety of massages, body treatments, and facials. Guests who receive treatments also get complimentary access to the hotel's pool deck.\n*   **My Spa Joy:** This wellness destination, located in a converted home in the Heights, offers customized treatments.\n\n"
          }
        ],
